<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Talker" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Talker,</orth> one who talks much, a prattler: <cit><quote>I'll grow a t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 1.1.110" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 1, 110</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--s are no good doers,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.352" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 352</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I be not found a t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.2.79" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 2, 79</bibl></cit>.
